ery","example","existingreferrals","expectedarrivaldate","expecteddeparturedate","false","filter","filtered","first","following","for","forename","formats","get","give","grade","h1","has","hmpps","identified","important","in","incoming","information","integer","interacting","interface","interfaces","involved","is","issues","it’s","json","key","keyworker","keyworkers","last","linked","list","make","making","managed","managing","managingcase","maps","may","members","message","messages","middlename","multiple","name","nametyperequireddescriptionschema","need","none","number","numberofelements","object","of","offset","ok","on","openapi","or","order","other","page","pageable","pageableobject","paged","pagenumber","pagesize","pagestaffresponse","parameterintyperequireddescription","parameters","part","path","personname","policy","practitioner","premises","premises.application.assessed","premises.application.submitted","present","probation","process","processed","progress","progressive","provide","query","queue","raised","real","record","records","reference","referral","referraldate","referrals","related","relevant","requested","requests","required","respond","responds","responses","role","role_approved_premises_staff","roles","schemas","screen","secured","separate","service","size","sort","sorted","sortobject","source","spec","sqs","staff","staffcode","staffgrade","staffresponse","stages","statusdescriptionschema","string","submitted","supplied","support","supporting","surname","swagger","team","teamcoderesponse","teamcodes","teams","technical","that","the","these","time","to","totalelements","totalpages","tree","triggers","true","type","ui","unpaged","unsorted","up","used","user","users","v1.0","various","via","view","we","when","who","with","workers","workload","yaml"],"pipeline":["trimmer"]}, "docs": {"11":{"title":"API Reference","content":"\n    \n    API Reference\n\n\n.technical-documentation \u003e h1 { display: none !important }\nThe following documentation is also available in these formats:\n\n\nOpenAPI JSON\nOpenAPI YAML\nSwagger UI\n\nAPI Reference v1.0\n\n\n\n\n\n\n/teams/managingCase/{crn}\n\nget\n\n  List all teams involved in managing the probation case\n\n\n  A probation case may be managed by staff members who\n            are associated with multiple teams in Delius. Approve Premises users\n            need to view all applications that may be covered by direct colleagues\n            in order to cover absence and other workload-related issues. Respond\n            with a list of every team code that covers the probation case identified\n            by the CRN to enable the Approved Premises service to present the\n            relevant list of Approved Premises applications to it’s users.\n\n\n\n\nParameters\n\n\nParameterInTypeRequiredDescription\n\n\n\n\ncrn\npath\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n\n\n\n\nstaffCode\nquery\nstring\nfalse\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nResponses\n\n\nStatusDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\n200\n\nOK\n\n\n\n{\n  \"teamCodes\": [\n    {\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\n\n\nTeamCodeResponse\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n/probation-case/{crn}/referrals\n\nget\n\n\n\n\nParameters\n\n\nParameterInTypeRequiredDescription\n\n\n\n\ncrn\npath\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nResponses\n\n\nStatusDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\n200\n\nOK\n\n\n\n{\n  \"crn\": \"string\",\n  \"referrals\": [\n    {\n      \"referralDate\": \"string\",\n      \"expectedArrivalDate\": \"string\",\n      \"expectedDepartureDate\": \"string\",\n      \"decisionDate\": \"string\",\n      \"approvedPremises\": {\n        \"description\": \"string\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\n\n\nExistingReferrals\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n/approved-premises/{code}/staff\n\nget\n\n  List all members of staff that are keyworkers in the Approved Premises\n\n\n  An Approved Premises is defined in Delius as part of reference data.\n            Probation staff members can be linked to an Approved Premises as either staff\n            members or keyworkers via the “Approved Premises and Teams” screen of the Delius\n            user interface. Keyworkers are defined via the “Approved Premises and Key Workers”\n            screen of the Delius user interface. Respond with a list of all members of staff\n            defined as keyworkers for the Approved Premises identified by the requested code.\n\n\n\n\nParameters\n\n\nParameterInTypeRequiredDescription\n\n\n\n\ncode\npath\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n\n\n\n\nkeyWorker\nquery\nboolean\nfalse\n\n\n\n\n\n\npageable\nquery\nobject\nfalse\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nResponses\n\n\nStatusDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\n200\n\nOK\n\n\n\n{\n  \"totalPages\": \"integer\",\n  \"totalElements\": \"integer\",\n  \"size\": \"integer\",\n  \"content\": [\n    {\n      \"code\": \"string\",\n      \"name\": {\n        \"forename\": \"string\",\n        \"surname\": \"string\",\n        \"middleName\": \"string\"\n      },\n      \"grade\": {\n        \"code\": \"string\",\n        \"description\": \"string\"\n      },\n      \"keyWorker\": \"boolean\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"number\": \"integer\",\n  \"sort\": {\n    \"empty\": \"boolean\",\n    \"sorted\": \"boolean\",\n    \"unsorted\": \"boolean\"\n  },\n  \"first\": \"boolean\",\n  \"last\": \"boolean\",\n  \"numberOfElements\": \"integer\",\n  \"pageable\": {\n    \"offset\": \"integer\",\n    \"sort\": {\n      \"empty\": \"boolean\",\n      \"sorted\": \"boolean\",\n      \"unsorted\": \"boolean\"\n    },\n    \"paged\": \"boolean\",\n    \"pageNumber\": \"integer\",\n    \"pageSize\": \"integer\",\n    \"unpaged\": \"boolean\"\n  },\n  \"empty\": \"boolean\"\n}\n\n\n\nPageStaffResponse\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nSchemas\nTeamCodeResponse\n\n\n\n\nNameTypeRequiredDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\nteamCodes\narray\ntrue\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\nApReferral\n\n\n\n\nNameTypeRequiredDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\nreferralDate\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nexpectedArrivalDate\nstring\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nexpectedDepartureDate\nstring\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\ndecisionDate\nstring\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\napprovedPremises\nobject\ntrue\n\n\n  ApprovedPremises\n\n\n\n\n\n\nApprovedPremises\n\n\n\n\nNameTypeRequiredDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\ndescription\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\nExistingReferrals\n\n\n\n\nNameTypeRequiredDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\ncrn\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nreferrals\narray\ntrue\n\n\n  ApReferral\n\n\n\n\n\n\nPageable\n\n\n\n\nNameTypeRequiredDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\npage\ninteger\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nsize\ninteger\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nsort\narray\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\nPageStaffResponse\n\n\n\n\nNameTypeRequiredDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\ntotalPages\ninteger\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\ntotalElements\ninteger\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nsize\ninteger\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\ncontent\narray\nfalse\n\n\n  StaffResponse\n\n\n\n\nnumber\ninteger\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nsort\nobject\nfalse\n\n\n  SortObject\n\n\n\n\nfirst\nboolean\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nlast\nboolean\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nnumberOfElements\ninteger\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\npageable\nobject\nfalse\n\n\n  PageableObject\n\n\n\n\nempty\nboolean\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\nPageableObject\n\n\n\n\nNameTypeRequiredDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\noffset\ninteger\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nsort\nobject\nfalse\n\n\n  SortObject\n\n\n\n\npaged\nboolean\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\npageNumber\ninteger\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\npageSize\ninteger\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nunpaged\nboolean\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\nPersonName\n\n\n\n\nNameTypeRequiredDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\nforename\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nsurname\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nmiddleName\nstring\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\nSortObject\n\n\n\n\nNameTypeRequiredDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\nempty\nboolean\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nsorted\nboolean\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nunsorted\nboolean\nfalse\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\nStaffGrade\n\n\n\n\nNameTypeRequiredDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\ncode\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\ndescription\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\nStaffResponse\n\n\n\n\nNameTypeRequiredDescriptionSchema\n\n\n\n\ncode\nstring\ntrue\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\nname\nobject\ntrue\n\n\n  PersonName\n\n\n\n\ngrade\nobject\nfalse\n\n\n  StaffGrade\n\n\n\n\nkeyWorker\nboolean\ntrue\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","url":"/api-reference.html"},"13":{"title":"AsyncAPI Reference","content":"ASyncAPI Reference\n\n\nASyncAPI Spec\n\n","url":"/async-api-reference.html"},"14":{"title":"About","content":"Approved Premises and Delius\nService that responds to Approved Premises domain events, calls the\nHMPPS Approved Premises API\nand records referral progress against the probation case record in Delius. We\nalso provide an API to give probation case information to support making\napproved premises referrals.\nBusiness Need\nSupporting the Approved Premises service with the correct information required\nto make an Approved Premises application and ensuring the Probation\nPractitioner has an up-to-date view of activity in the Approved Premises\nservice when interacting with the probation case via Delius.\nContext Maps\n\nInterfaces\nMessage Formats\nThe service responds to various HMPPS Domain Event message via the\nApproved Premises and Delius Queue.\nThe events are raised by the HMPPS Approved Premises Service\nto communicate important events in the approved premises referrals process.\nExample messages are in the development source tree.\nIncoming messages are filtered on eventType by the SQS queue policy\nEvent Triggers\nApproved Premises domain events are raised in real time as approved premises\nreferrals are processed. The progressive stages of a referral are raised as\nseparate events\n\n        \n          \nBusiness Event\nMessage Class\nMessage Event Type / Filter\n\nA referral to an approved premises has been assessed\nHMPPS Domain Event\n“approved-premises.application.assessed”\n\nA referral to an approved premises has been submitted\nHMPPS Domain Event\n“approved-premises.application.submitted”\n\n        \n      Authorisation\nAPI endpoints are secured by roles supplied by the HMPPS Auth client used in\nthe requests\n\n        \n          \nAPI Endpoint\nRequired Role\n\n/approved-premises/{code}/staff\nROLE_APPROVED_PREMISES_STAFF\n\n/teams/managingCase/{crn}\nROLE_APPROVED_PREMISES_STAFF\n\n        \n      ","url":"/"}}}